{"tid":413083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完套西謊極落有感而拍","createTime":"2017-09-25T08:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T10:17:55.000Z","uid":113545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc61b95a0deab8d056f4e2896d114c29871459aa","tid":413083,"uid":113545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:17:57.000Z","msg":"早兩日睇咗西謊極落：太爆太子太空艙<br />\n行出戲院之後嗰種個抑鬱仲滲緊出黎，於是突然就拎部手機出嚟拍咗幾嘢。<br />\n順便試下部新買嘅手機拍片效果點<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係打手，套戲又唔係真係咁高質，不過睇完有啲感受想舒發吓<br />\n短片入面啲「咗」、「嘅」、「喺」唔知點解字幕打唔到正字，有怪莫怪。<br />\n我係新手嚟咋，拍得唔好就見笑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好害羞呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/getreadyforacrazyfuture/videos/1524845890956332/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgetreadyforacrazyfuture%2Fvideos%2F1524845890956332%2F&d=yT8x7Aq%2F5ss%2Bamssk%2Fwf8Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a276fbee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/getreadyforacrazyfuture/videos/1524845890956332/</a>"},{"pid":"f2ca8658ae489599393c39e380be0da16f827425","tid":413083,"uid":113545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762e584580c551d02f3c158bb1b25e0d27bda73f","tid":413083,"uid":113545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}